data.description: Great home in very desirable location convenient to Hurlburt Field and Eglin Air Force Base. Huge yard backs to the Eglin Reservation for ultimate privacy. Enjoy grilling and entertaining on the large rear deck. Double door entry leads to large living room featuring a vaulted ceiling and fireplace. Good cabinet and counter space in the kitchen with a walk-in pantry and wet bar. Beautiful hardwood flooring in kitchen, dining room, foyer and  bedrooms with travertine in the living room and sun room. Large master bedroom offers bath with dual sinks and marble jetted tub. Inside laundry room with cabinets for extra storage. Hot water heater was installed in 2022, HVAC in 2011 and roof in 2019. The home is wired for a generator which is included for peace of mind. Ready for occupancy!
